code: protected Endpoint createEndpoint(String uri, String remaining, Map<String, Object> parameters) throws Exception {     RedisConfiguration configuration = new RedisConfiguration().     setHostAndPort(configuration, remaining).     setProperties(configuration, parameters).     RedisEndpoint endpoint = new RedisEndpoint(uri, this, configuration).     return endpoint. }

private void setHostAndPort(RedisConfiguration configuration, String remaining) {     String[] hostAndPort = remaining.split(":").     if (hostAndPort.length > 0 && hostAndPort[0].length() > 0) {         configuration.setHost(hostAndPort[0]).     }     if (hostAndPort.length > 1 && hostAndPort[1].length() > 0) {         configuration.setPort(Integer.parseInt(hostAndPort[1])).     } }
